{"tid":265442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 鄰居受傷 唔肯入返屋 有圖","createTime":"2017-05-31T15:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T16:57:53.000Z","uid":109589,"like":10,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"542b38946a1c15127b732b46fef7e627dcab9b53","tid":265442,"uid":109589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n我鄰居住我屋企出面既磚牆狹縫中間<br />\n<br />\n平時都有同佢打個招呼記 <br />\n佢都唔會同我揮手say hi 幾nice <br />\n有次落雨冇鎖匙入<br />\n佢都陪我 聽下我講嘢<br />\n<br />\n今日啱啱返到屋企<br />\n睇到佢落跌喺地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面兩隻腳斷咗冇反應<br />\n咁我咪墊起佢睇下佢有冇事<br />\n佢奄奄一息咁樣 冇乜反應<br />\n我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xhf8k7ou\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxhf8k7ou&h=dc2bda1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢跌左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/epgi5mj0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fepgi5mj0&h=b912ebd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0vro2ekz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0vro2ekz&h=7de0c947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢住既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d631aa3f247edd228db595e376546a6978f53c49","tid":265442,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"你肯定斷嘅係腳 唔係手？"},{"pid":"56f7e9c944daf34cbd67fd8d16fb93ba657cd444","tid":265442,"uid":278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"幫佢做人工呼吸救返起條命仔先"},{"pid":"72abe4aae75b01ef4e8d188e65542f59a993aaf8",